                                                        <span class="text">Simple time tracking extension which helps you be more productive</span>
                                                    </a>
                                                </li>
                                                <li>
                                                    <a href="https://tmetric.com/download#mobile-apps-section">
                                                        <strong class="title">Mobile apps</strong>
                                                        <span class="text">Install TMetric app to your phone or a tablet device. Android and iOS platforms are supported.</span>
                                                    </a>
                                                </li>
                                                <li>
                                                    <a href="https://tmetric.com/download">
